# Keep the build context small + reproducible. The image runs a fresh
# `pnpm install` and builds shared -> web -> server inside the build stage,
# so host node_modules / dist artifacts must NOT leak in — a stale server/dist
# would otherwise ship pre-deletion compiled routes and crash the app.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.git
.gitignore
.env
.env.*
*.local
pnpm-store
.superpowers
.claude
docs
*.md
!README.md
*.log
.DS_Store
